snippet.title: Tamarin Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Leap with the agility of a tamarin as you journey into the Northern wilderness on scenic routes through forests, fjords and mountains. Along the way you will chase mysterious electrical fireflies, discover a secret underground world of dancing ants, rescue innocent birds, and restore the tamarins’ once idyllic natural habitat.

More info, screenshots and preorder: http://tamaringame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/chameleon_games
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/chameleongames.ltd
